These are Puzzles for 1x4 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-2-1::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: gospel, blues, folk, punk
1. the fan of blues is between the fan of folk and the fan of punk##2
2. the fan of blues is on the left of the fan of folk##1
3. the fan of gospel is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |  2   |  3   |   4   |
| Music-Genre   | gospel | punk | blues | folk |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-2-2::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: fanta, lemonade, milk, soy-milk
1. the person drinking soy-milk is on the right of the person drinking lemonade##1
2. the person drinking milk is on the right of the person drinking fanta##1
3. the person drinking soy-milk is between the person drinking lemonade and the person drinking fanta##2

.:: Answer ::.
|            |       1       |    2    |  3   |    4     |
| Beverage   | lemonade | soy-milk | fanta | milk |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-2-3::.
4 different pets are kept: rabbit, chinchilla, fish, snake
1. the owner of the snake is on the right of the owner of the rabbit##1
2. the owner of the fish is between the owner of the chinchilla and the owner of the snake##2
3. the owner of the rabbit is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|       |  1   |   2    |  3   |   4    |
| Pet   | rabbit | snake | fish | chinchilla |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-2-4::.
There 4 different types of food: broccoli, banana, kiwi, mango
1. the person eating kiwi is between the person eating banana and the person eating broccoli##2
2. the person eating broccoli is on the right of the person eating kiwi##1
3. the person eating banana is on the right of the person eating mango##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |     1      |     2     |   3    |     4     |
| Food   | mango | banana | kiwi | broccoli |

