.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-2-20::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: iced-tea, juice, water, sprite
1. the person drinking iced-tea is between the person drinking water and the person drinking juice##2
2. the person drinking juice is on the left of the person drinking sprite##1
3. the person drinking juice is on the right of the person drinking iced-tea##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |  1   |      2      |   3    |    4    |
| Beverage   | water | iced-tea | juice | sprite |

 